The paper discusses techniques for initial access in 5G mmWave cellular networks, which involves communication and networking aspects. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The paper also involves information theory (cs.IT), millimeter-wave technology (cs.MM), and algorithms (cs.AR) for optimizing the initial access process. Additionally, the paper performs a coverage and delay analysis, which involves mathematical modeling and optimization (cs.MA).
